## How It Connects

```
User ──── Favorite.user ────► Favorite ◄──── Favorite.property ──── Property
                              { user, property, createdAt }
                              unique index prevents duplicates
```

- Every `Favorite` document is just two ObjectId references + timestamps
- When fetching a user's list, `property` is populated with full listing details + the agent's contact info — **one query, no extra calls needed**

