## Quick Testing Guide

**Login first** (session cookie is required for all favorites endpoints):
```
POST /api/auth/login
{ "email": "...", "password": "..." }
```

**Save a property (replace with a real property ID from your DB):**
```
POST /api/favorites/684abc000000000000000001
```

**Press again — it should toggle off:**
```
POST /api/favorites/684abc000000000000000001
```

**View your saved list:**
```
GET /api/favorites
```

**Check saved state (for a specific property):**
```
GET /api/favorites/684abc000000000000000001/status
```

**Explicitly remove:**
```
DELETE /api/favorites/684abc000000000000000001
```

**Test unauthenticated (no cookie — should return 401):**
```
GET /api/favorites
→ 401 { "message": "You must be logged in to access this resource." }
```
